    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入<strong>Rogue Battalion</strong>的战略混乱之中，这是一款以二战为灵感的独特自走棋游戏，将战术决策与爆炸性的战场动作相融合。指挥日益壮大的部队，面对源源不断的敌军，部署部队并运用强大的技能来扭转战局。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态自走棋玩法</strong> <br>在你专注于高层策略时，观赏部队在激烈的自动化交战中厮杀。明智地选择单位，调整战术，赢取胜利！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/e19621795ed967f286577829e09e3beb.poster.avif?t=1763849042\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/e19621795ed967f286577829e09e3beb.webm?t=1763849042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/e19621795ed967f286577829e09e3beb.mp4?t=1763849042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>用特殊技能掌控战局</strong><br>利用强大的支援技能来扭转局势！呼叫毁灭性的炮击、召唤关键的空投补给，或在危急时刻部署增援。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/b95c58a1c7e1e398bafd6532412e9eb2.poster.avif?t=1763849042\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/b95c58a1c7e1e398bafd6532412e9eb2.webm?t=1763849042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/b95c58a1c7e1e398bafd6532412e9eb2.mp4?t=1763849042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不断进化的小队自定义</strong><br>在每波之间，从随机出现的部队中选择来扩充军力。是加强前线，增派狙击手提供远程支援，还是部署反坦克部队来对抗敌方装甲？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/ec95c1a37649374340061bbbc5f5cf4f.poster.avif?t=1763849042\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/ec95c1a37649374340061bbbc5f5cf4f.webm?t=1763849042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/ec95c1a37649374340061bbbc5f5cf4f.mp4?t=1763849042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级你的武器库</strong><br>在每次游戏过程中，使用获得的<strong>补给</strong>进行升级。增强士兵、强化支援技能，并尝试各种策略来应对更加艰巨的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/2899ed334d700f4294dabbb93b8969d3.poster.avif?t=1763849042\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/2899ed334d700f4294dabbb93b8969d3.webm?t=1763849042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/2899ed334d700f4294dabbb93b8969d3.mp4?t=1763849042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>长期策略的元进度</strong><br>在多次游玩之间不断解锁，利用可叠加的小型增益来强化初始部队，并适用于所有游戏。每一次游戏都能让你更接近最终胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/47d870a7c1a1a2553cb0c97bffd8a4a6.poster.avif?t=1763849042\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/47d870a7c1a1a2553cb0c97bffd8a4a6.webm?t=1763849042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/47d870a7c1a1a2553cb0c97bffd8a4a6.mp4?t=1763849042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>二战氛围</strong><br>沉浸在充满硝烟味的二战环境和标志性武器中，以独特的艺术风格呈现。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/963f19198f781a7b935ed296bac1ff0b.poster.avif?t=1763849042\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/963f19198f781a7b935ed296bac1ff0b.webm?t=1763849042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/963f19198f781a7b935ed296bac1ff0b.mp4?t=1763849042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沙盒模式</strong><br>通过自定义对战来享受乐趣，随心所欲地部署部队，创造史诗级甚至“乱斗”般的战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/7805a75bd828a3e2c2b82e3ddb35ad83.poster.avif?t=1763849042\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/7805a75bd828a3e2c2b82e3ddb35ad83.webm?t=1763849042\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222240/extras/7805a75bd828a3e2c2b82e3ddb35ad83.mp4?t=1763849042\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你能坚守阵地多久？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会迎接挑战并带领你的部队取得胜利，还是会被源源不断的敌军瓦解信念？<strong>Rogue Battalion</strong>拥有无尽的可重玩性、不断演变的策略，以及令人满意的战术战斗与资源管理融合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择一名指挥官。组建你的军队。升级部队。整编军力。赢得这场战争！</p>",
